    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n8150" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πυκάζω</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πύκα</span>), opt. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πυκάζοιεν</span>,
          aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πύκασα</span>, pass. perf. part.
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πεπυκασμένος</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">cover
            closely</span> or <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">thickly, wrap up;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τινὰ νεφέλῃ</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 17.551</span></i>; of a helmet, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πύκασε
            κάρη,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Il. 10.271</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">
            σφέας αὐτούς</span>, ‘crowd’ themselves, <i><span class="en">Od. 12.225</span></i>; pass., of chariots ‘overlaid’
          with gold, etc., <i><span class="en">Il. 23.503</span></i>; met., of
          grief, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τινὰ φρένας</span>, ‘overshadow’ the
          soul, <i><span class="en">Il. 8.124</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
